# Akechi Goro

## Background

A high school detective nicknamed "The Second Coming of the Detective Prince" on the way to kill Joker at the interrogation room but somehow fell into DST world. Can he survive a world full of monsters?

## Stats

 * Health 200
 * Hunger 200
 * Sanity 100

## Perks

 * SIG-Sauer P230 suppressed
   - Long range, 100 damage
   - Feed system, 8-round magazine (.32 ACP)
 * Killer instinct
   - Sanity increases 8 points per kill
 * Trust no one
   - Akechi's sanity reduce 0.5 point per second around other people
 * Stay fit
   - Eat less, hunger point reduce slower
